name: Dinah Foley
bio: Dinah Foley is a comedian in Portland, Oregon, noted for her squirrelly feminism and sharp elbows. She has performed on shows at Curious Comedy Theater, The Doug Fir, New Deal Distillery, Helium Comedy Club and has written more than one thing on Reductress and Portland's late night talk show Late Night Action. Among her credits are SF Sketchfest, opening for Bernie Sanders at the Moda Center, the NW Womenâ€™s Comedy Festival, Siren Nation, and .20 cents at the Hoot Loot slot machine at the Indian Head Casino in Warm Springs.
